.TH LOGRIFLE 1
.SH NAME
logrifle \- A Console-based Log Viewer
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B logrifle
[options]
.IR file1 
[
.IR file2
[ ... 
.IR fileN
]]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B logrifle
is a free console-based logviewer written in java that is designed to "rifle through" large logfiles.
.SH USING LOGRIFLE
.TP
For a detailed descriptions of the options, type: \fBlogrifle --help\fR 

